Description:
Live in luxury, Play in the park
With a bedroom for everyone & living spaces for all, this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, multi-zoned home puts the focus on an entertaining lifestyle. Corner-sited in compact grounds overlooking Gunn Reserve this spacious house is finished to the highest quality with jarrah floors, granite benchtops & deluxe appointments (heating, cooling, vacuum, alarm, intercom, double auto-garage). Dual living/dining areas flow around an elite Euro appliance kitchen & out to paved gardens, while the 1st-floor includes a sublime master with WIR & dual vanity ensuite. two double size bedrooms & huge 4th bedroom with 2nd WIR - large enough to be another living space...just a walk to the station, a moment to the shops!
4 bedrooms with robes, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 WIRs
dual living/dining, Smeg kitchen, double garage
heating, cooling, vacuum, alarm, intercom
views across EE Gunn Res, walk to station

Description:
Period beauty, pool & a Zone position
Splash out, Zone in, make great family living your Mission! In a leafy street just 3 blocks from Ormond Shopping strip & station, this solid-brick Spanish Mission beauty on a wide and deep allotment 60'x 150' (9,000sqft) or 18.3m x 45.7m (835sqm) extends to offer a flexible 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom floorplan with gracious formal lounge & dining rooms, relaxed family living & al fresco fun with paved entertaining out by a heated pool (with spa-seat) & a separate hot tub. Rich with period features (including lavish leadlight, decorative ceilings, two fireplaces & original timberwork) & updated with modern comforts including new stainless-steel appliances for the country-style kitchen, ducted heating & double carport, you can't miss this McKinnon College Zone Mission beauty!
3 bedrooms with robes, 2 bathrooms
formal & family living, ducted heating
heated pool, hot-tub, double carport
McKinnon College Zone, near strip & station

Description:
Impressively renovated unit
Singles, couples as well as investors will see the value in this exceptionally well renovated first floor unit. Situated within a well maintained block, the unit comprises a well equipped new kitchen with stainless steel Bosch appliances, and matched by the stunning bathroom that also combines the laundry into the same place. For living and entertaining there is a lounge with balcony, while accommodation comes from the bedroom with built in wardrobe. As new the space of 2!
This is a 1 bedroom apartment with 2 many benefits to list! Strictly speaking this as-new apartment classifies as a 1 bedroom floorplan, but in reality a well-sized, naturally-lit "study" is set to double as a 2nd bedroom. But the sizeable extras don't end there. With balconies front & rear (one for living, one for the robe-fitted master), a sleek CaesarStone kitchen with European appliances (including dishwasher) & a European laundry separate to the large marble-finished bathroom, this high-quality apartment is optioned up! There's reverse-cycle air-con, intercom entry & a secure basement garage with store...even the location is 2 good to be true - just a minute from station & shops.

Description:
Gracious, spacious & In Zone
Corner a rare Victorian within a walk of station, shops & the College! Set on a College Zone corner, this enchanting Victorian offers surprising 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom space & superb period detail. Graced with leadlight & beautiful fireplaces, this original charmer stars a large lounge beneath an elaborate pressed-metal ceiling, family living beneath a soaring vaulted roofline & a pretty ensuite beside the master bedroom. Beautifully detailed with a farmhouse sink for the classic timber-benchtop kitchen & glossy newly polished boards, the enticing living even extends to the garden with a teenager retreat/5th bedroom & home-office in traditional outbuildings around the auto-entry carport.
up to 5 bedrooms, sep home-office, 2 bathrooms
lounge, soaring family zone, st-st app kitchen
secure auto-entry carport, heating, air-con
walk to shops & station in McKinnon College Zone

Description:
Edwardian with a zone address
Combining perfect period beauty with a prized McKinnon College Zone address, this picturesque Edwardian is set to charm with family-wise 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom accommodation & the ideal mix of formal & family spaces. Renovated with respect for original detail (including lovely leadlight, beautiful baltic pine & fantastic fretwork) , this appealing home offers gracious living with a tiled fireplace for formal living/dining, a timber benchtop & stainless-steel appliance kitchen for the family zone, & a wisteria-draped canopy for the al fresco area. Centrally heated, fully alarmed & set in family-sized gardens that are paved for easy care, this is a pretty perfect educational opportunity.
3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, st-st app kitchen
formal, family & al fresco areas, offstreet parking
central heating, alarm, approx 4935sqft/458sqm garden
Zone address, walk to Ormond & McKinnon stations

Description:
Pure period grace & a McKinnon Zoned address
Make a premier College Zone address your Mission! Proximity to leading schools, including McKinnon College, makes this period residence so desirable. On 680sqm approx this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom light-filled Spanish Mission home is a rare find in the area. Beyond fine formal rooms, light & spacious family living flows from a timeless timber kitchen to a sun-bathed northerly deck, while a cleverly zoned plan places master-suite (with frameless-screened ensuite & WIR) away from kids' bedrooms in a quiet rear wing. With a secure garage in lush tank-watered surrounds, this gracious residence combines rich period detail (including story-book leadlight windows, elaborate ceilings & fireplaces) with modern comforts ...and one of the area's most family-wise addresses.
4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, (ensuite), WIR
lounge, dining, light-filled family zone, garage
timber kitchen, duct heating, rev-cyc air-con
4,600L water-storage, McKinnon College Zone
